  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Automated software analysis now allows for quick estimation of cardiac output from the
      echocardiographic 5-chamber view. This study will validate the automated software method
      against pulmonary artery thermodilution and against conventional cardiac output measurement
      with echocardiography.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
